{"tid":1588291,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲：䆁放梁天琦\"破解\"流水鬥爭術","createTime":"2019-09-22T17:46:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T08:04:28.000Z","uid":45336,"like":4,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"83fdd1f8874a90f4ada0c00f2fff979ed5d466f1","tid":1588291,"uid":45336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T17:46:26.000Z","msg":"陳雲：關鍵人物梁天琦，林鄭月娥看得起。目前香港的亂局，特區政府苦無對策。然而政府忽視了一個重要現象：港獨情緒。民眾呼喊「光復香港，時代革命」和高唱港獨國歌，是因為港獨情緒無法發洩和代理。<br />\n港獨的關鍵，在於一個關鍵人物梁天琦。他目前被關天牢，備受泛民消費及代理，令民間抗爭的港獨情緒積壓而無法代表。<br />\n港府破解流水鬥爭術的方法很簡單，就是釋放梁天琦，領導民眾與政府對話，解決不言不語的流水鬥爭術。<br />\n港府釋放戴耀庭及黃之鋒，卻未釋放梁天琦，是極不公平的，也令港獨支持者憤憤不平。只要港府用特赦、假釋或保外就醫的方法將梁天琦釋放出獄，民間的意氣得到宣洩，鬥爭起碼消退八九成。<br />\n快，十月一日之前，特首林鄭月娥無論如何都要將梁天琦弄出來，化解流水鬥爭，令習近平總書記放心。<br />\n（按：請港獨派廣傳，等梁天琦可以釋放。先放出來再算吧。圖片來源：網絡）<br />\n閱讀智力門檻：IQ110."},{"pid":"64e9e2e78dbcde74cb6891167f61a9714270a294","tid":1588291,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T17:46:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"eb55b86e20d0620da2c1ff019b7d4dbeb6743fc1","tid":1588291,"uid":185018,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T17:47:31.000Z","msg":"可憐的陳云根，永遠活在梁天琦的陰影下"},{"pid":"88f17bd24392e654faee0bb87b305ed2c9c6b48b","tid":1588291,"uid":29080,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"eb55b86e20d0620da2c1ff019b7d4dbeb6743fc1","tid":1588291,"uid":185018,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T17:47:31.000Z","msg":"可憐的陳云根，永遠活在梁天琦的陰影下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T17:50:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abb07af1b7de809ebbc8440fd8ad778d7737d9b9","tid":1588291,"uid":205275,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T01:06:26.000Z","msg":"唔小心正評左<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0443f75f7d7aad9ddfe9d0612373b31061079deb","tid":1588291,"uid":131121,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb55b86e20d0620da2c1ff019b7d4dbeb6743fc1","tid":1588291,"uid":185018,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T17:47:31.000Z","msg":"可憐的陳云根，永遠活在梁天琦的陰影下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T01:12:07.000Z","msg":"咪推陳雲遧垃圾post ok?"},{"pid":"546be91f408efc94d19e64f5806651063e85c628","tid":1588291,"uid":259244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T03:52:47.000Z","msg":"係咪諗多左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"722a75ce9e6c881ac2a653b65b754a5ab961f3ac","tid":1588291,"uid":264400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T08:04:28.000Z","msg":"佢指既「梁天崎」係冇面具既領頭人"}]}